                <p>
				The New House was completed in 1997.  It is the newest guest house at Quailridge.  It has four large bedrooms, two of which contain two beds each.  All bedrooms have private bathrooms.  The house also has a partial kitchen and dining area, a living room with fireplace and  satellite TV, and a covered front porch with rockers.
				</p>
                
                <p>
                The Horkin House is one of Quailridge's traditional guest houses.  It contains four bedrooms, two baths, kitchen/bar, large living room with a fireplace, satellite TV, front porch, and even a hot-tub.
                </p>
                
                <div>
                <ul class="nobullet">
                <li><%= image_tag("lodge31.jpg") %></li>
