                </div>
                
                <p>
                The Old Main Lodge is the original building at Quailridge.  It has just undergone a complete renovation to be a comfortable guest house with five bedrooms, four bathrooms, a partial kitchen, and living room with  a fireplace and satellite TV.  From its front deck there is a relaxing view of lake Dot, a great fishing spot.
                </p>
                
                <p>
                All of the facilities have been designed to offer our guests all the conveniences of home but without the bother. Everything is within easy walking distance.  Housekeepers take care of the daily clean-up, linens and towels.  Our staff takes pride in making your hunting experience at Quailridge truly memorable.
				</p>
                
